tr: high quality porcelain originally made only in China
dishware made of high quality porcelain

value.def: China is a hard white substance made from clay. It is used to make things such as cups, bowls, plates, and ornaments.

example.ex: Judy collects blue and white china.

value.def: Cups, bowls, plates, and ornaments made of china are referred to as china .

data.enText: white clay which is baked and used for making delicate cups, plates, etc.
cups, plates, etc. that are made of china
She got out the best china.
a bull in a china shop
a person who is careless, or who moves or acts in a rough or awkward way, in a place or situation where skill and care are needed
data.chText: （不顾环境）笨拙莽撞的人，冒失鬼
